1
00:00:49,620 --> 00:00:53,820
=Camellias=

2
00:00:53,860 --> 00:00:56,780
=Episode 5=

3
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:58,759
(Trying to run?)

4
00:01:38,319 --> 00:01:39,200
Why you?

5
00:01:40,680 --> 00:01:43,200
To see what tricks
you have up your sleeve,

6
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:45,480
of course.

7
00:01:48,319 --> 00:01:49,840
How did you find this place?

8
00:01:52,560 --> 00:01:54,439
I can't touch you,

9
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:56,920
but I can touch others.

10
00:01:58,920 --> 00:02:01,239
Faking his death was to free him.

11
00:02:02,680 --> 00:02:04,319
I misjudged you, My Lord.

12
00:02:05,040 --> 00:02:06,920
Since the Nanfeng Pavilion

13
00:02:06,920 --> 00:02:08,639
is no pleasure den,

14
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:11,319
then what is it really?

15
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:13,360
You pry into my affairs like this,

16
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,759
aren't you afraid I'll kill you?

17
00:02:24,000 --> 00:02:24,960
You won't.

18
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:30,400
You risked your reputation

19
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:33,159
to save those harmed by Zhu Yunqi.

20
00:02:33,719 --> 00:02:34,960
So kind-hearted.

21
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,960
You'd never really hurt me.

22
00:02:40,360 --> 00:02:41,360
I warn you,

23
00:02:41,520 --> 00:02:43,560
if my secrets ever leak,

24
00:02:44,039 --> 00:02:45,520
I will kill you.

25
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,360
My Lord,

26
00:02:57,240 --> 00:02:58,759
some secrets

27
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,639
aren't meant to be sold.

28
00:03:03,439 --> 00:03:04,599
They're meant

29
00:03:04,960 --> 00:03:07,159
to bring us

30
00:03:08,039 --> 00:03:09,439
closer.

31
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:13,280
From now on,

32
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:15,479
you don't have to carry it all alone.

33
00:03:24,759 --> 00:03:25,400
Fine.

34
00:03:27,120 --> 00:03:28,199
Since you're not afraid to die,

35
00:03:28,199 --> 00:03:29,520
then play along with me.

36
00:03:37,199 --> 00:03:38,280
These past two days,

37
00:03:38,719 --> 00:03:40,960
her dancing has improved.

38
00:03:42,120 --> 00:03:43,120
My Lord,

39
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:45,479
are you really presenting

40
00:03:45,479 --> 00:03:46,800
the Holy Maiden to His Majesty?

41
00:03:46,960 --> 00:03:48,280
If you change your mind now,

42
00:03:48,280 --> 00:03:49,280
it's not too late.

43
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:02,000
Judging by your gaze,

44
00:04:02,000 --> 00:04:03,080
today

45
00:04:03,080 --> 00:04:04,800
will surely be a victory.

46
00:04:07,039 --> 00:04:08,240
Don't get cocky.

47
00:04:08,479 --> 00:04:09,919
A thousand blooms,

48
00:04:09,919 --> 00:04:11,360
a sea of flowers.

49
00:04:11,840 --> 00:04:13,240
His Majesty has seen

50
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,639
countless women.

51
00:04:15,039 --> 00:04:16,519
If you have no unique edge,

52
00:04:17,240 --> 00:04:18,639
he won't even remember you.

53
00:04:19,319 --> 00:04:20,040
Also,

54
00:04:20,399 --> 00:04:21,959
Rong Zhaohua will be there today.

55
00:04:22,759 --> 00:04:23,639
Remember.

56
00:04:23,639 --> 00:04:24,480
Stay calm,

57
00:04:24,480 --> 00:04:26,079
and don't ruin my plan.

58
00:04:28,079 --> 00:04:30,720
Even if you doubt me,

59
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:31,800
you should trust

60
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:33,160
your own skill in training.

61
00:04:34,199 --> 00:04:36,920
If you're still uneasy, My Lord...

62
00:04:46,839 --> 00:04:48,319
This is a blood bond.

63
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:49,680
With it,

64
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:50,759
between us,

65
00:04:50,759 --> 00:04:53,399
the Divine Power will briefly linger.

66
00:04:53,759 --> 00:04:54,639
Like

67
00:04:54,639 --> 00:04:56,560
twin phoenixes,

68
00:04:56,879 --> 00:04:58,480
we are one in spirit.

69
00:04:58,480 --> 00:05:01,639
You'll know my every move, My Lord.

70
00:05:04,399 --> 00:05:04,920
Let's go.

71
00:05:11,759 --> 00:05:15,000
The noble ladies' performances
begin soon.

72
00:05:15,000 --> 00:05:15,879
Ladies,

73
00:05:15,879 --> 00:05:18,639
proceed in the order

74
00:05:18,639 --> 00:05:21,439
set beforehand.

75
00:05:33,319 --> 00:05:35,160
Please wait a moment, my lady.

76
00:05:35,160 --> 00:05:36,519
You're up next.

77
00:05:36,920 --> 00:05:38,240
You may all leave now.

78
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,360
Yes.

79
00:05:43,839 --> 00:05:45,519
(Though I don't know)

80
00:05:45,519 --> 00:05:48,519
(why he and Zhu Yunqi are at odds,)

81
00:05:49,120 --> 00:05:52,240
(from what I've seen of him lately,)

82
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:54,040
(he seems trustworthy.)

83
00:05:54,399 --> 00:05:56,199
(For now, I'll follow his plan.)

84
00:06:07,519 --> 00:06:08,879
Rong Zhaohua.

85
00:06:27,639 --> 00:06:28,839
(She's alone.)

86
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:31,040
(It's a rare chance.)

87
00:06:48,040 --> 00:06:50,160
(I've seen this place
in my sister's memories.)

88
00:07:07,439 --> 00:07:09,600
(This is where she was abused.)

89
00:07:44,439 --> 00:07:46,319
(Daring to show yourself here?)

90
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:51,279
(Why is my Divine Power...)

91
00:08:00,879 --> 00:08:02,800
Do you like this place?

92
00:08:04,199 --> 00:08:06,000
I built it

93
00:08:06,000 --> 00:08:08,759
especially for your sister.

94
00:08:08,759 --> 00:08:11,120
Too bad she was useless.

95
00:08:11,319 --> 00:08:12,759
Didn't take long

96
00:08:13,319 --> 00:08:15,800
before she died by my hand.

97
00:08:17,120 --> 00:08:19,439
If your sister couldn't beat me,

98
00:08:20,240 --> 00:08:22,120
how could you?

99
00:08:23,560 --> 00:08:25,000
Stay put.

100
00:08:26,279 --> 00:08:28,079
When I have time,

101
00:08:29,680 --> 00:08:31,240
I'll deal with you.

102
00:08:33,559 --> 00:08:35,919
(Diligence in Governance)
Where's the next lady? She's so late.

103
00:08:43,559 --> 00:08:45,519
His Majesty is the supreme ruler.

104
00:08:46,159 --> 00:08:48,039
Who does this lady think she is,

105
00:08:48,759 --> 00:08:50,440
keeping him waiting?

106
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,360
I wonder how

107
00:08:54,360 --> 00:08:56,279
you train these ladies.

108
00:08:56,279 --> 00:08:58,000
So utterly lacking in manners.

109
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,600
Does he

110
00:09:23,600 --> 00:09:25,559
treat the palace like his own yard,

111
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:27,480
daring to act so brazen
before His Majesty?

112
00:09:27,480 --> 00:09:29,080
Might need a pair of silver shackles

113
00:09:29,080 --> 00:09:31,919
to ease His Majesty's frustration.

114
00:09:39,559 --> 00:09:41,879
(So this is where my sister was trapped.)

115
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,960
My Lord!

116
00:09:53,559 --> 00:09:55,960
Thank goodness for the blood bond.

117
00:09:55,960 --> 00:09:57,679
It led me straight to you.

118
00:10:02,919 --> 00:10:03,679
My Lord,

119
00:10:04,720 --> 00:10:05,200
your hands...

120
00:10:05,200 --> 00:10:06,039
Don't worry about it.

121
00:10:08,519 --> 00:10:10,240
I will get you out of here.

122
00:10:10,900 --> 00:10:12,420
(Diligence in Governance,
Trust in the Virtuous)

123
00:10:24,440 --> 00:10:26,039
Your Majesty must be tired.

124
00:10:26,039 --> 00:10:27,440
Best return to your chambers.

125
00:10:27,759 --> 00:10:28,279
Indeed.

126
00:10:28,600 --> 00:10:29,279
Your Majesty,

127
00:10:29,759 --> 00:10:30,679
please rest now.

128
00:10:36,220 --> 00:10:38,540
(Diligence in Governance,
Trust in the Virtuous)

129
00:10:40,360 --> 00:10:42,440
Jiang Yukui, Holy Maiden

130
00:10:42,440 --> 00:10:46,240
of the Zhao Tribe,
dances for Your Majesty.

131
00:10:49,399 --> 00:10:50,480
(Impossible.)

132
00:10:51,460 --> 00:10:52,900
ظآزA cup of wineظآز

133
00:10:52,900 --> 00:10:54,300
ظآزA stick of incenseظآز

134
00:10:54,300 --> 00:10:57,500
ظآزA handful of coins
to judge life and deathظآز

135
00:10:57,500 --> 00:10:58,780
ظآزA pair of candlesظآز

136
00:10:58,860 --> 00:11:00,060
ظآزA single hairpinظآز

137
00:11:00,500 --> 00:11:03,060
ظآزA marriage bond on paper,
but who will stayظآز

138
00:11:03,060 --> 00:11:05,900
ظآزEach step brings an endingظآز

139
00:11:09,820 --> 00:11:11,620
ظآزWhy hasn't he come yetظآز

140
00:11:11,620 --> 00:11:12,900
ظآزWhy hasn't he come yetظآز

141
00:11:12,900 --> 00:11:13,860
ظآزThen I'll go aloneظآز

142
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:15,500
ظآزDown this endless road
through the nightظآز

143
00:11:15,500 --> 00:11:16,780
ظآزShe sees himظآز

144
00:11:16,780 --> 00:11:19,780
ظآزDressed in red,
with tears as her celebrationظآز

145
00:11:19,900 --> 00:11:22,940
ظآزVermilion adorns a tragic smileظآز

146
00:11:22,940 --> 00:11:25,940
ظآزInto her hands,
an urn of bones is placedظآز

147
00:11:25,940 --> 00:11:29,180
ظآزHandle it gently,
what hardship is thereظآز

148
00:11:29,180 --> 00:11:32,180
ظآزShe sheds the red, now clothed in whiteظآز

149
00:11:32,180 --> 00:11:34,900
ظآزBridal red turns funeral white,
her heart shatteredظآز

150
00:11:34,900 --> 00:11:36,420
ظآزHis fate remains unknownظآز

151
00:11:36,420 --> 00:11:37,860
ظآزYet she won't accept itظآز

152
00:11:37,860 --> 00:11:38,740
ظآزFor his sakeظآز

153
00:11:38,740 --> 00:11:40,940
ظآزShe'll walk this endless road
through the nightظآز

154
00:11:42,159 --> 00:11:44,200
(What's going on?)

155
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:55,940
ظآزWe fell in love, but met too lateظآز

156
00:11:55,940 --> 00:11:57,580
ظآزBorn in troubled timesظآز

157
00:11:57,620 --> 00:12:00,500
ظآزIn haste, you left me
only an umbrellaظآز

158
00:12:00,500 --> 00:12:02,140
ظآزThree years of longing,
five years of waitingظآز

159
00:12:02,140 --> 00:12:03,940
ظآزThe plum blossom knows not
the bamboo horse's painظآز

160
00:12:03,940 --> 00:12:06,140
ظآزThe old steed returns,
but you never doظآز

161
00:12:06,159 --> 00:12:07,720
(You are a child of fate, My Lord,)

162
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:10,279
(yet even you are bound by pain.)

163
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:12,600
(If you transfer that pain to me,)

164
00:12:13,159 --> 00:12:14,519
(you'll be unburdened.)

165
00:12:15,440 --> 00:12:16,559
(But if we do that,)

166
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:17,559
(you'll be in agony.)

167
00:12:18,140 --> 00:12:19,220
ظآزShe sees himظآز

168
00:12:19,519 --> 00:12:21,080
(Compared to what I've endured,)

169
00:12:21,240 --> 00:12:22,559
(this pain is nothing.)

170
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:25,039
(If I don't get out today,)

171
00:12:25,639 --> 00:12:27,159
(all my plans for revenge)

172
00:12:27,759 --> 00:12:29,120
(will go up in flames.)

173
00:12:30,960 --> 00:12:32,879
(Please trust me, My Lord.)

174
00:12:34,740 --> 00:12:37,300
ظآزBridal red turns funeral white,
her heart shatteredظآز

175
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:38,900
ظآزHis fate remains unknownظآز

176
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,300
ظآزYet she won't accept itظآز

177
00:12:40,300 --> 00:12:41,300
ظآزFor his sakeظآز

178
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:43,220
ظآزShe'll walk this endless road
through the nightظآز

179
00:12:43,220 --> 00:12:44,060
ظآزShe sees himظآز

180
00:12:44,399 --> 00:12:45,039
(What's wrong?)

181
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:46,799
(No.)

182
00:12:47,159 --> 00:12:48,600
(You need to trust me completely)

183
00:12:48,600 --> 00:12:50,080
(for me to read your mind)

184
00:12:50,639 --> 00:12:52,080
(and complete the transfer.)

185
00:12:53,340 --> 00:12:56,420
ظآزHandle it gently,
what hardship is thereظآز

186
00:12:56,420 --> 00:12:59,340
ظآزShe sheds the red,
now clothed in whiteظآز

187
00:12:59,340 --> 00:13:02,140
ظآزBridal red turns funeral white,
her heart shatteredظآز

188
00:13:02,140 --> 00:13:03,660
ظآزHis fate remains unknownظآز

189
00:13:03,660 --> 00:13:05,140
ظآزYet she won't accept itظآز

190
00:13:05,140 --> 00:13:06,100
ظآزFor his sakeظآز

191
00:13:06,100 --> 00:13:08,060
ظآزShe'll walk this endless road
through the nightظآز

192
00:13:08,060 --> 00:13:08,679
ظآزShe sees himظآز

193
00:13:08,679 --> 00:13:09,799
(This is...)

194
00:13:14,480 --> 00:13:15,480
(Pleasure.)

195
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:16,919
(Jiang Yukui.)

196
00:13:17,039 --> 00:13:17,879
(My Lord,)

197
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,519
(some secrets)

198
00:13:19,519 --> 00:13:21,080
(aren't meant to be sold.)

199
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,759
(Mutual benefit)

200
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:24,799
(is the way to last.)

201
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:29,559
(I was only trying to serve you.)

202
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:31,360
(I only wish)

203
00:13:31,600 --> 00:13:33,320
(to serve you, My Lord.)

204
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:36,600
(I can help you.)

205
00:13:40,240 --> 00:13:41,360
(Why?)

206
00:13:41,919 --> 00:13:44,320
(His recent memories are all of me.)

207
00:14:03,100 --> 00:14:04,500
ظآزThe moon sinks in the westظآز

208
00:14:04,980 --> 00:14:06,420
ظآزThe cold lamp burns lowظآز

209
00:14:06,620 --> 00:14:09,740
ظآزNo one knocks upon the mountain gateظآز

210
00:14:10,060 --> 00:14:13,860
ظآزSnow-white winds and moonlight
touch me firstظآز

211
00:14:16,820 --> 00:14:18,540
ظآزPear blossoms fill the courtyardظآز

212
00:14:18,540 --> 00:14:20,060
ظآزYet love and hate entwineظآز

213
00:14:20,420 --> 00:14:23,820
ظآزBound by precepts,
yet craving worldly desiresظآز

214
00:14:23,820 --> 00:14:27,820
ظآزGathering red beans
for half a lifetimeظآز

215
00:14:28,980 --> 00:14:32,140
ظآزThe Buddha speaks of countless pathsظآز

216
00:14:32,140 --> 00:14:35,700
ظآزHow can one glance spanning ages
save a wandering soulظآز

217
00:14:35,700 --> 00:14:38,020
ظآزTrapped within
the space between your browsظآز

218
00:14:38,020 --> 00:14:42,220
ظآزFalling deeper and deeperظآز

219
00:14:42,660 --> 00:14:44,300
ظآزThe green lamp sheds no lightظآز

220
00:14:44,300 --> 00:14:45,820
ظآزUpon one who entered the pathظآز

221
00:14:45,820 --> 00:14:49,020
ظآزThe six senses cannot cleanse
the dust of the pastظآز

222
00:14:49,420 --> 00:14:51,340
ظآزIn dreams, it's youظآز

223
00:14:51,340 --> 00:14:52,740
ظآزBeyond dreams, no oneظآز

224
00:14:52,740 --> 00:14:56,060
ظآزClinging to one obsession,
adrift in a sea of sufferingظآز

225
00:14:56,060 --> 00:14:59,460
ظآزI can't forget the stars in your eyesظآز

226
00:14:59,460 --> 00:15:03,020
ظآزOur fate had already taken rootظآز

227
00:15:03,020 --> 00:15:06,260
ظآزIn this mortal world, there is only usظآز

228
00:15:06,260 --> 00:15:09,700
ظآزHopelessly bound by loveظآز
